      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a superior balance of performance and value. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience characterized by mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic. A premier choice for the discerning driver seeking reliability without compromise.",
      "price": 34800.0,
