    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it\u2019s been such a fantastic vehicle for me. It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs smoothly, and has been well-taken care of over the years. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for a new owner to get behind the wheel. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This example retains its high-revving character with crisp throttle response via individual throttle bodies. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity under lateral load. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the factory M-Variable differential lock. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-maintained driver, the suspension geometry remains tight with updated bushings and Bilstein dampers. A true enthusiast\u2019s spec focused on tactile feedback and longitudinal performance.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Well-maintained. Reliable performance. Clean title.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive form for its age. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with a consistent idle, and the transmission shifts crisply through every gear. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you may find minor, typical road wear upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, featuring well-preserved upholstery and fully functional electronics. Recent service includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection to ensure it is road-ready. It strikes the perfect balance between a dependable daily driver and a well-cared-for enthusiast's car.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing an exceptional balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation. Offering a refined driving experience and a documented history of care, it stands as a premier selection for the discerning buyer seeking a high-caliber automobile. We invite you to experience the superior craftsmanship and dependable nature of this standout example firsthand.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend adventure, this beauty is ready to hit the road. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream\u2014I'd love for it to go to a great new home! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8. This high-revving, naturally aspirated unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear power band peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis features M-specific subframes and a five-link rear suspension setup, paired with the M Variable Differential Lock for superior mechanical grip and corner-exit traction. This example is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), allowing for precise adjustment of the damping rates. Recent service includes a diagnostic sweep of the rod bearings and throttle actuators to ensure peak operational integrity. A mechanically sound enthusiast's machine with sharp turn-in and visceral acoustic feedback.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
